description.displayText: Agnes did a fabulous job taking care of our two dogs and cleaning our home- I highly recommend her!!! Our dogs can be pretty high maintenance but she was very patient and took the time to do a pre visit to get to know them.  She is punctual, dependable, responsive, kind and she gave us plenty of updates on the dogs while we were away.  We came home to a clean home and happy dogs- we couldn't ask for more!! Look no further- you should hire Agnes for your pet sitting and housekeeping needs!!!

description.displayText: I connected w/ Agnes through Care.com and was immediately impressed with her after our phone interview. I hired her right after our in-person interview and she is by far the best housekeeper I have ever had! I'm almost afraid to write this since I don't want anyone to steal away her time from me! She is extremely professional and knowledgeable about all aspects of housecleaning. I have 2 kitties and she is able to get my apartment cat-hair free and sparkling clean. She is great w/ the kitties and doesn't mind that they follow her around the apartment. She is extremely thorough in her cleaning and does an excellent job with laundry also. I am super happy and impressed with her!  Thanks Agnes!

description.displayText: I recently connected with Agnes through Care.com, and I couldn't be more impressed by her skill and commitment. My home looks wonderful without me having to give any direction. Similar to the reviews of others, it's been an absolute pleasure to work with Agnes. She is kind, honest, responsive, flexible and easy to work with. I am very grateful to Agnes for all that she does. It's a huge relief to have found someone I can trust and who can help me. I look forward to continuing to work with her.

description.displayText: Agnes has come to my apartment once every 2 weeks for the past 2.5 years.  She has been wonderful.  She is very thorough and always willing to tailor the time she spends to specific areas that may need extra attention in a given week.  She always responds promptly to emails and texts and has always been accommodating when I have needed to move days around.  Agnes has been a pleasure and I look forward to continuing to work with her.
